Find the year anchor. Starting with year Y:
 - note the century anchor A
 - take the last two digits T = Y % 100
 - divide them by twelve D = T / 12
 - and take the reminder R = T % 12
 - the resulting increment is I = (D + R) + R/4
 - add the century anchor to get W = A + I

Find the weekday. Starting with date D:
 - note the year anchor W
 - this months doomsday is O
 - the resulting increment is I = D - O
 - add the year anchor to get R = W + I
